  3.815731961351335*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c36bae79-7efe-41df-b102-\
24d073cd2e13"],

Cell["\<\
This block of code helps you visualize setting up bounds in terms of \
\"Smashing\" or \"Constructing.\" The lines drawn in each diagram represent \
the lines related to the inner variable of integration.  You have to smash \
the inner variable of integration out of a problem before you can smash the \
outer variable of integration out. \
\>", "Text",
 ShowGroupOpener->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.4459135753939314`*^9, 
  3.44591367355508*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"4685eccd-0112-4cfd-a3f1-\
304d6f29009a"],

