Cell["\<\
The following code will draw a solid region described using triple integrals \
in Cartesian coordinates.  The code actually draws 6 surfaces (one for each \
inequality) and then puts them in the same plot. \
\>", "Text",
 ShowGroupOpener->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.750691353264286*^9, 3.7506914614726143`*^9}, {
  3.750692326196982*^9, 3.750692334741083*^9}, {3.750693024489408*^9, 
